Package voicesplitting.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GUIConstants
    The GUIConstants class holds constant values to be used for the GUI layout.
    HmmVoiceSplittingModelParametersDialog
    A VoiceSplittingParametersDialog object creates and displays the gui dialog which can be used to change the currently loaded HmmVoiceSplittingModelParameters.
    MidiNoteGUI
    A MidiNoteGUI object controls the GUI layout of a MidiNote.
    MidiNoteGUIMouseListener
    A MidiNoteGUIMouseListener controls the actions to be performed when a MidiNoteGUI object is clicked with the mouse.
    MidiNoteGUIPopupMenu
    A MidiNoteGUIPopupMenu represents the right-click menu for any MidiNoteGUI object.
    NoteDisplayer
    A NoteDisplayer is the JPanel that is able to display MidiNotes graphically.
    NoteDisplayerWorker
    A NoteDisplayerWorker does the work of updating the note displayer GUI in the background.
    VoiceSplittingGUI
    The BeatTrackingGUI is the class which creates the gui for the beat tracking project.
    VoiceSplittingGUIMenuBar
    A BeatTrackingGUIMenuBar is the MenuBar for the main BeatTracking GUI.
    VoiceSplittingRunner
    A BeatTrackingRunner is the class which interfaces between a VoiceSplittingGUI and the actual program logic.
